  "github_id": 8558351,
  "description": "<div class=\"Box-sc-62in7e-0 js-snippet-clipboard-copy-unpositioned DirectoryRichtextContent-module__SharedMarkdownContent__hHXUL\" data-hpc=\"true\"><article class=\"markdown-body entry-content container-lg\" itemprop=\"text\"><div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h1 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Advanced Analytics</h1><a id=\"user-content-advanced-analytics\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Advanced Analytics\" href=\"https://github.com/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics#advanced-analytics\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Adds detailed per-route analytics, historical tracking, and financial metrics to your network.<br/>\nAdvanced Analytics sits alongside the game UI and gives you data the base game doesn't expose:\n</p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><strong>Per-route metrics</strong> — ridership, throughput, capacity usage, transfer connections, revenue, cost, profit, and profit per train</li>\n<li><strong>Three data modes</strong> — live (last 24h), historical (end-of-day snapshots), and side-by-side day comparison</li>\n<li><strong>Trend charts</strong> — visualize how any route evolved over time</li>\n<li><strong>System map</strong> — schematic overview of your entire network</li>\n<li><strong>Storage manager</strong> — export, import, and manage analytics data across saves</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\">All data is stored in IndexedDB and persists across game restarts. No save file is modified.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://liberapay.com/Steno\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d8aa853ef98dae0fcb4899aa479be5b4abd0f0e656481d7da3c7a3388dac69f2/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f4c69626572617061792d537570706f72742d4636433931353f6c6f676f3d6c6962657261706179266c6f676f436f6c6f723d626c61636b\" alt=\"Liberapay\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Liberapay-Support-F6C915?logo=liberapay&amp;logoColor=black\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/Q5Q61VIM68\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img height=\"20\" style=\"height: 40px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b83b435a0fbb41274d1021b0d2747ae96c34c69f8cb51cc339b3eb5bbcca75a9/68747470733a2f2f73746f726167652e6b6f2d66692e636f6d2f63646e2f6b6f6669332e706e673f763d36\" alt=\"Buy Me a Coffee at ko-fi.com\" data-canonical-src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/kofi3.png?v=6\"></a></p>\n\n<hr>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Contributing</h2><a id=\"user-content-contributing\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Contributing\" href=\"https://github.com/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics#contributing\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Bug reports and feature suggestions are welcome.</p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><strong>Found a bug?</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics/issues/new\">Open an issue</a> with steps to reproduce and your game version.</li>\n<li><strong>Have an idea?</strong> Open an issue to discuss it before sending a PR.</li>\n<li><strong>Want to contribute code?</strong> Fork the repo, make your changes on a branch, and open a pull request against <code>master</code>. Please keep PRs focused — one feature or fix per PR.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Thank you</h2><a id=\"user-content-thank-you\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Thank you\" href=\"https://github.com/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics#thank-you\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">A big thank you to everyone who tested early builds, \nreported bugs, and shared feedback. This mod wouldn't be where it is \nwithout your support. ❤️</p>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">License</h2><a id=\"user-content-license\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: License\" href=\"https://github.com/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics#license\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://github.com/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics/blob/master/LICENSE\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/fb44a27e99163eb43672f5e277f6fbcfdf7bf14b1a74f79fb03861cab9ee6b1c/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f6c6963656e73652f73746566616e6f726967616e6f2f616476616e6365645f616e616c7974696373\" alt=\"License\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/stefanorigano/advanced_analytics\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a></p>\n</article></div>",
